'''水窗'''是指软[[X射线|X射线]]的[[波长|波长]]范围处在2.34[[nm|nm]]与4.4nm之间，前者对应[[氧|氧]]原子的[[K吸收带|K吸收带]]，后者对应[[碳|碳]]原子的K吸收带，即X射线光子能量范围在530[[eV|eV]]到280eV间．在此范围内，[[水|水]]不吸收X射线，即水对X射线是[[透明|透明]]的．但是，此范围内的X射线会被氮原子和其他构成[[生物|生物]]机体的[[元素|元素]]吸收，因此，该波长可用于对活体生物样本进行[[X射线显微|X射线显微]]<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://aip.scitation.org/doi/10.1063/1.1150151|pages=11–14|title=Feasibility tests of transmission x-ray photoelectron emission microscopy of wet samples|journal=Review of Scientific Instruments|volume=71|issue=1|author=Gelsomina De Stasio, B. Gilbert, T. Nelson, R. Hansen, J. Wallace, D. Mercanti, M. Capozi, P. A. Baudat, P. Perfetti, G. Margaritondo, B. P. Tonner|doi=10.1063/1.1150151|access-date=2018-04-02|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809013449/https://aip.scitation.org/doi/10.1063/1.1150151|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Generation of Coherent X-rays in the Water Window Using 5-Femtosecond Laser Pulses|journal=Science|date=1997-10-24|doi=10.1126/science.278.5338.661|url=http://science.sciencemag.org/content/278/5338/661|language=en|volume=278|issue=5338|pages=661–664|issn=0036-8075|accessdate=2018-04-02|author=Ch Spielmann, N. H. Burnett, S. Sartania, R. Koppitsch, M. Schnürer, C. Kan, M. Lenzner, P. Wobrauschek, F. Krausz|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180101102037/http://science.sciencemag.org/content/278/5338/661|archive-date=2018-01-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref>．

